{"tid":342173,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"男人應該點樣保養自己既皮膚？","createTime":"2017-07-31T11:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T16:54:47.000Z","uid":57958,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"10fdb8adc4cdce6f9d6360f8e507ffbce08dfdb7","tid":342173,"uid":57958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:37:16.000Z","msg":"呢排開始爆瘡...有時仲係囊腫性個隻，好耐先退，退完有印，好長手尾..<br />\n但我唔知原因<br />\n我之前係韓國成個月，日日夜訓食油炸野，皮膚都好好<br />\n一返香港就變差<br />\n係因為香港天氣太濕鳩？<br />\n<br />\n我而加護膚只係用番簡洗面<br />\n都用左成個幾月<br />\n洗完塊面真係完全冇油啜住咁制<br />\n但其實咁樣有冇問題？<br />\n<br />\n幾日前親戚買左支double D比我話有助去瘡，係咪真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己用左幾日好似效果不大<br />\n仲有咩應該要做#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14aeabd7d1ae550dc26265009fc2f70fd570ca04","tid":342173,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:38:29.000Z","msg":"屌你正正經經買枝洗面奶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"049bacf4c18bb56f23ac5ec366392166d624d6cb","tid":342173,"uid":57958,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:43:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你正正經經買枝洗面奶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前係用開洗面奶，但係塊面都係咁，所以先試下其他野.."},{"pid":"4bcebcb09665fd24a2b8e7154e78281066deb686","tid":342173,"uid":121130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T12:38:26.000Z","msg":"用番簡你今日先爛面你都汁到啦"},{"pid":"1a82d1981fff06ba699d608aaacf76e3a8dfb68e","tid":342173,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T12:41:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"180c29d4403d70fc168340a1bfcce8f26d7ad4a4","tid":342173,"uid":51890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T16:54:47.000Z","msg":"我都係用梘洗面，手工梘最好，其實咁先好"}]}